OL,3,CBloody Sunday Soldier F murder trail
OL,4,Cjudge rules hearsay evidence can be
OL,5,Cheard
OL,7,FA judge at Belfast Crown Court has
OL,8,Fruled that hearsay evidence in the
OL,9,Ftrial of Soldier F for the murder of
OL,10,Ftwo men during Bloody Sunday is
OL,11,Fadmissible.
OL,13,FJudge Patrick Lynch heard arguments
OL,14,Faround the evidence last week, which
OL,15,Fwas described as key, and includes
OL,16,Fstatements by two former soldiers
OL,17,Fgiven to the Royal Military Police in
OL,18,F1972 and to the Widgery Inquiry in the
OL,19,Fsame year.
