OL,4,Cjudge rules hearsay evidence can be
OL,5,Cheard
OL,7,FHis ruling today means the trial will
OL,8,Fcontinue.
OL,10,FSoldier F, who cannot be identified,
OL,11,Fis accused of murdering James Wray and
OL,12,FWilliam McKinney.
OL,14,FHe is also charged with five attempted
OL,15,Fmurders during the incident in Derry's
OL,16,FBogside area, namely of Joseph Friel,
OL,17,FMichael Quinn, Joe Mahon, Patrick
OL,18,FO'Donnell and a person unknown.
OL,20,FHe has pleaded not guilty to the seven
OL,21,Fcounts.
