OL,7,FThe trial opened last week and heard
OL,8,Fstatements of a number of people
OL,9,Fpresent at the shootings, including
OL,10,Fformer Stormont MP Ivan Cooper, who
OL,11,Fhad organised the preceding civil
OL,12,Frights march through Derry.
OL,14,FSoldier F is attending court each day
OL,15,Fof the non-jury trial, behind a
OL,16,Fcurtain to protect his anonymity,
OL,17,Fwhile members of the Wray and McKinney
OL,18,Ffamilies and supporters watch on from
OL,19,Fthe public gallery.
