OL,7,FBloody Sunday was one of the most
OL,8,Fnotorious incidents of the Northern
OL,9,FIreland Troubles.
OL,11,FThirteen people were killed on the day
OL,12,Fand another man shot by paratroopers
OL,13,Fdied four months later.
OL,15,FMany consider him the 14th victim of
OL,16,FBloody Sunday but his death was
OL,17,Fformally attributed to an inoperable
OL,18,Fbrain tumour.
