OL,7,FPolice in Northern Ireland launched a
OL,8,Fmurder investigation after the
OL,9,Flandmark Saville Inquiry, which
OL,10,Freported in 2010, found there was no
OL,11,Fjustification for shooting any of
OL,12,Fthose killed or wounded.
OL,14,FAt the time of the inquiry's
OL,15,Fpublication, then-prime minister David
OL,16,FCameron issued a public apology,
OL,17,Fsaying the killings were "unjustified
OL,18,Fand unjustifiable".
